<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 1698/70 of the Commission of 25 August 1970 on certain derogations concerning the production of quality wines produced in specified regions </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1698/70 m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonnas valmistatud kvaliteetveinide tootmist k&auml;sitlevate teatavate erandite kohta 25. august 1970 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Community; Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 817/70 (1) of 28 April 1970 laying down special provisions for quality wines produced in specified regions, and in particular Articles 5 (3) and 16 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 28. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 817/70, milles s&auml;testatakse m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonnas valmistatud kvaliteetveine k&auml;sitlevad eris&auml;tted, eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 3 ja artiklit 16, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 817/70 provides that the processing of grapes into must and of must into wine should take place within the specified region where those grapes were harvested in order that the wine produced may be designated a quality wine p.s.r.; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 817/70 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et viinamarjade t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine viinamarjavirdeks ja viinamarjavirde t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine veiniks peaks toimuma selles m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonnas, kus k&otilde;nealused viinamarjad koristati, et toodetud veini saaks nimetada mpv-kvaliteetveiniks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is necessary to define certain of the conditions to which the quality wines p.s.r. referred to in the second subparagraph of Article 5 (1) (a) of Regulation (EEC) No 817/70 are subject; </inglise>
<eesti> on vaja m&auml;&auml;ratleda teatavad tingimused, mida m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 817/70 artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti a teises l&otilde;igus osutatud mpv-kvaliteetveinid peavad t&auml;itma; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas there are, however, cases where Member States may authorise wine production outside the specified region of production; whereas it is necessary, because of the risks of misrepresentation involved in such a practice, to limit it to cases where the grapes and grape musts are made into quality wines p.s.r. in the immediate proximity of the specified region; </inglise>
<eesti> teatavatel juhtudel v&otilde;ivad liikmesriigid siiski lubada veini tootmist v&auml;ljaspool m&auml;&auml;ratletud tootmispiirkonda; pettuse ohu t&otilde;ttu on selline praktika vaja piirata juhtudega, kus viinamarjad ja viinamarjavirded t&ouml;&ouml;deldakse mpv-kvaliteetveiniks m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonna vahetus l&auml;heduses; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to ensure effective control of such practice, provision should be made for it to be subject to application by the interested party and for the Member States to adopt measures on the storage and movement of these products, on the making of wine from those products, as well as entries in the turnover records; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuse praktika t&otilde;husa kontrollimise tagamiseks tuleks s&auml;testada, et huvitatud pool peab taotlema k&otilde;nealuse praktika rakendamiseks luba ja liikmesriigid peavad v&otilde;tma vastu meetmed, mis k&auml;sitlevad k&otilde;nealuste toodete ladustamist ja liikumist, k&otilde;nealustest toodetest veini tootmist ning k&auml;ibearvestust; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, where basic products intended for wine production under the conditions provided for in this Regulation are being dispatched from one Member State to another, a special entry should be made in the documents referred to in Article 39 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 542/69 (2) of 18 March 1969 on Community transit and in Article 1 of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2313/69 (3) of 19 November 1969 on the internal Community transit document laid down for the purpose of certifying the Community nature of goods </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud tingimustel veini tootmiseks etten&auml;htud p&otilde;hisaaduste l&auml;hetamisel &uuml;hest liikmesriigist teise tuleks n&otilde;ukogu 18. m&auml;rtsi 1969. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 542/69 (&uuml;henduse transiidi kohta) artiklis 39 ja komisjoni 19. novembri 1969. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2313/69 (kaupade &uuml;henduse laadi t&otilde;endamiseks etten&auml;htud &uuml;henduse sisetransiidi dokumendi kohta) artiklis 1 nimetatud dokumentidesse teha erikanne; sellisel juhul puudub vajadus komisjoni 25. augusti 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1699/70 (veinisektori teatavate toodete kontrollimise kohta) artikliga 2 etten&auml;htud erikannete j&auml;rele; </eesti>
<inglise> ; whereas, in this case, there is no need for the special entries provided for in Article 2 of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1699/70 (4) of 25 August 1970 on the control of certain products in the wine sector; </inglise>
<eesti> pettusekatsete v&auml;ltimiseks ja kontrolli h&otilde;lbustamiseks tuleks s&auml;testada, et viinamarjad ja viinamarjavirded, mille kohta kehtib k&otilde;nealune erand, hoitaks mpv-kvaliteetveinide tootmiseks sobimatutest viinamarjadest ja viinamarjavirretest eraldi; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to avoid any attempt at misrepresentation and to facilitate control, provision should be made for the grapes and musts which are the subject of this derogation to be held separately from grapes and grape musts which are unsuitable for yielding quality wines p.s.r.; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjonile tuleks teatada kogused, mille kohta kehtivad m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 817/70 artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti a teise l&otilde;iguga etten&auml;htud erandid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Commission should be informed of the quantities which are the subject of the derogations provided for in the second subparagraph of Article 5 (1) (a) of Regulation (EEC) No 817/70; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las veinituru korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
