<inglise> "Producer Member State" within the meaning of the second subparagraph of Article 5 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 817/70, means the Member State on whose territory the grapes to be made into wine were harvested. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootjaliikmesriik m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 817/70 artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 2 teises l&otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;ratletud t&auml;henduses on liikmesriik, mille territooriumil veiniks t&ouml;&ouml;deldavad viinamarjad koristati. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The competent authorities of the producer Member States may grant authorisation for the processing referred to in Article 1 only to wine makers using grapes or grape musts intended for processing into a quality wine p.s.r. and if their establishment is situated in the immediate proximity of the specified region in question. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootjaliikmesriigi p&auml;dev asutus v&otilde;ib anda artiklis 1 nimetatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise loa &uuml;ksnes nendele veinivalmistajatele, kes kasutavad mpv-kvaliteetveiniks t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks etten&auml;htud viinamarju v&otilde;i viinamarjavirdeid ja kelle ettev&otilde;te asub k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonna vahetus l&auml;heduses. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Any party, whether an individual or a group, interested in obtaining such authorisation shall submit an application therefor to the competent authority of the producer Member State. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga sellise loa saamisest huvitatud &uuml;ksikisik v&otilde;i r&uuml;hm esitab loa taotluse tootjaliikmesriigi p&auml;devale asutusele. </eesti>
<inglise> The authorisation once granted shall remain valid until withdrawn by the competent authority or until the person authorised states in writing that he is no longer producing a quality wine p.s.r. outside the specified region. </inglise>
<eesti> Antud luba kehtib, kuni p&auml;dev asutus tunnistab selle kehtetuks v&otilde;i kuni loa saanud isik kinnitab kirjalikult, et ta ei tooda enam mpv-kvaliteetveini v&auml;ljaspool m&auml;&auml;ratletud piirkonda. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The grapes and grape musts referred to in Article 1 must be held separately from grapes and grape musts which are unsuitable for yielding quality wines p.s.r. </inglise>
